'''塔米尔·莱斯枪杀案'''于2014年11月22日发生在[[美国|美国]][[俄亥俄州|俄亥俄州]][[克里夫蘭_(俄亥俄州)|克里夫兰市]]。事件造成了时年12岁的男孩塔米尔·莱斯（Tamir Rice，2002年6月25日－2014年11月23日）死亡。

事故中，两名警察，26岁的蒂莫西·鲁曼（{{lang|en|Timothy Loehmann}}）和46岁的弗兰克·贾姆柏克（{{lang|en|Frank Garmback}}），在接到调度中心关于城市公园中“有一名黑人男性坐在秋千上用[[手枪|手枪]]瞄准路人”的报告后赶往现场<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kqBqg43WN34|title=Tamir Rice Shooting - Cleveland Police Dispatch Radio|work=Youtube|author=WEWS NewsChannel5|date=2014-11-24|accessdate=2016-01-04|archive-date=2015-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150808140207/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kqBqg43WN34|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Washington Post">{{cite news|last1=Izadi|first1=Elahe|last2=Holley|first2=Peter|title=Video shows Cleveland officer shooting 12-year-old Tamir Rice within seconds|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/news/post-nation/wp/2014/11/26/officials-release-video-names-in-fatal-police-shooting-of-12-year-old-cleveland-boy/|accessdate=2014-11-26|work=The Washington Post|date=2014-11-26|archive-date=2021-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227170312/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/post-nation/wp/2014/11/26/officials-release-video-names-in-fatal-police-shooting-of-12-year-old-cleveland-boy/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|first=Tom|last=McCarthy|url=http://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2014/nov/26/tamir-rice-video-shows-boy-shot-police-cleveland|title=Tamir Rice: video shows boy, 12, shot 'seconds' after police confronted child|work=[[衛報|The Guardian]]|date=2014-11-26|accessdate=2016-01-04|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304061115/http://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2014/nov/26/tamir-rice-video-shows-boy-shot-police-cleveland|dead-url=no}}</ref>。一名报警人在电话中描述了一名男性在库德尔休闲公园（{{lang|en|Cudell Recreation Center}}）拿着“手枪”随机地瞄准行人。在报警电话开头和中间，报警人两次提到手枪“有可能是假的”<ref name="LA Times">{{cite news|author=Los Angeles Times staff|url=http://www.latimes.com/nation/nationnow/la-na-nn-tamir-rice-911-call-20141126-htmlstory.html|title=Hear the 911 call about Tamir Rice: Gun is 'probably fake,' caller says|date=2014-11-26|accessdate=2016-01-04|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125040832/https://www.latimes.com/nation/nationnow/la-na-nn-tamir-rice-911-call-20141126-htmlstory.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在报警电话的结尾，报警人认为“他可能是未成年人”<ref name="LA Times"></ref>。尽管如此，这些信息没能在调度中心第一次与鲁曼和贾姆柏克联系时被反馈给二人<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/news/national/12-year-old-tamir-rice-shot-cleveland-autopsy-article-1.2043229|title=Cleveland cop who killed 12-year-old Tamir Rice not told boy’s age|publisher=Daily News|author=[[美联社|THE ASSOCIATED PRESS]]|date=2014-12-13|accessdate=2016-01-04|archive-date=2021-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210501205402/https://www.nydailynews.com/news/national/12-year-old-tamir-rice-shot-cleveland-autopsy-article-1.2043229|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.newsnet5.com/news/local-news/cleveland-metro/tamir-rice-shooting-officers-were-not-told-the-gun-could-be-fake-or-that-suspect-was-juvenile|title=Tamir Rice shooting: Officers were not told the gun could be fake or that suspect was juvenile|publisher=newsnet5.com - Cleveland|date=2014-11-24|accessdate=2016-01-04|first=Nikki|last=Ferrell|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160217055731/http://www.newsnet5.com/news/local-news/cleveland-metro/tamir-rice-shooting-officers-were-not-told-the-gun-could-be-fake-or-that-suspect-was-juvenile|archivedate=2016-02-17}}</ref>。两名警官后来在报告中表示，莱斯在他们到达现场后有将枪从腰带中拔出的动作。在到达现场两秒钟后，鲁曼在警车停稳之前向莱斯开枪两次，击中了莱斯的躯干部位<ref name="Washington Post" /><ref>{{cite news|title=Cleveland Police name Timothy Loehmann, officer who shot Tamir Rice, 12, on west side|last=Ferrell|first=Nikki|url=http://www.newsnet5.com/news/local-news/cleveland-metro/cleveland-police-name-timothy-loehmann-officer-who-shot-tamir-rice-12-on-west-side|publisher=Scripps TV Station Group|date=2014-11-26|accessdate=2014-11-27|archive-date=2016-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160816055107/http://www.newsnet5.com/news/local-news/cleveland-metro/cleveland-police-name-timothy-loehmann-officer-who-shot-tamir-rice-12-on-west-side|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="scribd.com">{{cite web|url=http://www.scribd.com/doc/268410100/Judgement-entry-on-Tamir-Rice-case|title=Judgement entry on Tamir Rice case|website=scribd.com|accessdate=2016-01-04|publisher=WKYC.com|archive-date=2016-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307023218/https://www.scribd.com/doc/268410100/Judgement-entry-on-Tamir-Rice-case|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="dailykos.com">{{cite news|url=http://www.dailykos.com/story/2014/12/04/1349386/-New-lie-in-the-shooting-death-of-Tamir-Rice-discovered-Police-never-saw-the-tip-of-the-gun-at-all|date=2014-12-04|title=New lie in the shooting death of Tamir Rice discovered: Police never saw the tip of the gun at all|accessdate=2016-01-04|first=Shaun|last=King|publisher=Daily Kos|archive-date=2017-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170421092924/http://www.dailykos.com/story/2014/12/04/1349386/-New-lie-in-the-shooting-death-of-Tamir-Rice-discovered-Police-never-saw-the-tip-of-the-gun-at-all|dead-url=no}}</ref>。两名警察在开枪后均没有对莱斯进行现场[[急救|急救]]。莱斯在事发后第二天在城市健康医疗中心（MetroHealth Medical Center）去世<ref name="MacDonald">{{cite news|last1=MacDonald|first1=Evan|title=Cause of death released for 12-year-old boy shot by Cleveland police|url=http://www.cleveland.com/metro/index.ssf/2014/11/cause_of_death_released_for_12.html|accessdate=2014-11-26|date=2014-11-24|archive-date=2018-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181206134418/https://www.cleveland.com/metro/index.ssf/2014/11/cause_of_death_released_for_12.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

莱斯的枪后来被证实是没有橙色记号的[[软气枪|软气枪]]（仿真枪枪口有橙色记号），而不是真的手枪<ref name="Fitzsimmons">{{cite news|last=Fitzsimmons|first=Emma|date=2014-11-23|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2014/11/24/us/boy-12-dies-after-being-shot-by-cleveland-police-officer.html|title=12-Year-Old Boy Dies After Police in Cleveland Shoot Him|accessdate=2016-01-04|work=The New York Times|archive-date=2021-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210210084549/https://www.nytimes.com/2014/11/24/us/boy-12-dies-after-being-shot-by-cleveland-police-officer.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="BBC24">{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-30172433|title=Tamir Rice: US police kill boy, 12, carrying replica gun|work=BBC|date=2014-11-24|accessdate=2016-01-04|archive-date=2021-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210210084501/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-30172433|dead-url=no}}</ref>。4天之后，也就是2014年11月26日，警方公布了现场的监控资料<ref name="Protests break out in Cleveland over Tamir Rice shooting, Ferguson grand jury decision">{{cite web|url=http://www.cleveland.com/metro/index.ssf/2014/11/protests_break_out_in_cleveland.html|title=Protests break out in Cleveland over Tamir Rice shooting, Ferguson grand jury decision|date=2014-11-25|accessdate=2016-01-04|work=cleveland.com|first=Ryllie|last=Danylko|archive-date=2018-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180727111753/https://www.cleveland.com/metro/index.ssf/2014/11/protests_break_out_in_cleveland.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年6月3日，警长办公室发表声明，表示他们对于事件的调查已经结束，相关的资料已经转交给了[[公诉|公诉]]机关。公诉人向[[大陪审团|大陪审团]]展示了这些证据，但是[[陪审团|陪审团]]作出了无罪判决<ref name="nobill">{{cite web|url=http://www.wkyc.com/story/news/local/cleveland/2015/06/03/tamir-rice-investigation-complete-to-be-handed-over-to-prosecutor/28406351/|title=Tamir Rice investigation complete, going to prosecutor|first=Ryan|last=Haidet|date=2015-06-03|accessdate=2016-01-04|work=WKYC}}{{Dead link|date=2018年8月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref name="auto">{{cite web|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/tamir-rice-inductment_56818253e4b0b958f65a0909?ir=Black%2BVoices&section=black-voices&utm_campaign=122815&utm_medium=email&utm_source=Alert-black-voices&utm_content=FullStory&ncid=newsltushpmg00000003|title=No Indictment For Cop Who Fatally Shot 12-Year-Old Tamir Rice|first=Kim|last=Bellware|date=2015-12-28|accessdate=2016-01-04|website=Huffington Post|archive-date=2015-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151231060204/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/tamir-rice-inductment_56818253e4b0b958f65a0909?ir=Black+Voices&section=black-voices&utm_campaign=122815&utm_medium=email&utm_source=Alert-black-voices&utm_content=FullStory&ncid=newsltushpmg00000003|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在这件事发生以后，有媒体报道鲁曼之前在俄亥俄州独立市担任警察期间曾被诊断为情绪不稳定，不适合入伍或者任职[[警察|警察]]<ref name=LATimes.unfit>{{cite web|last1=Mai-Duc|first1=Christine|title=Cleveland officer who killed Tamir Rice had been deemed unfit for duty|url=http://www.latimes.com/nation/nationnow/la-na-nn-cleveland-tamir-rice-timothy-loehmann-20141203-story.html|work=Los Angeles Times|accessdate=2014-12-05|date=2014-12-03|archive-date=2022-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220127024650/https://www.latimes.com/nation/nationnow/la-na-nn-cleveland-tamir-rice-timothy-loehmann-20141203-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。这一事件得到了美国和世界媒体的关注，其中部分原因是这件事件发生的时间距离之前几起警察枪杀黑人男性的事件间隔不久。

== 事件过程 ==
一名坐在[[公园|公园]]隔壁[[露台|露台]]的报警人向911描述道：有一名疑似[[青少年|青少年]]的人在库德尔休闲公园（{{lang|en|Cudell Recreation Center}}）拿着“手枪”随机指向周围的人。报警人曾两次提到“手枪”可能是假的<ref name="Cleveland police officer shot Tamir Rice immediately after leaving moving patrol car">{{cite web|url=http://www.cleveland.com/metro/index.ssf/2014/11/cleveland_police_officer_shot_1.html|title=Cleveland police officer shot Tamir Rice immediately after leaving moving patrol car|first=Brandon|last=Blackwell|date=2014-11-26|accessdate=2016-01-04|website=cleveland.com|archive-date=2019-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190114122705/https://www.cleveland.com/metro/index.ssf/2014/11/cleveland_police_officer_shot_1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。警方发言人表示在接到调度指示时，不清楚两名警官是否得知手枪的真假。事后，经过调查，除了提到“手枪”以外，调度员并没有向两名警官解释枪的真假<ref name="Fitzsimmons"></ref><ref name="Video Shows Cleveland Cop Shoot 12-Year-Old Tamir Rice Within Seconds">{{cite web|url=http://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/video-shows-cleveland-cop-shoot-12-year-old-tamir-rice-n256656|title=Video Shows Cleveland Cop Shoot 12-Year-Old Tamir Rice Within Seconds|first=Tracy|last=Connor|date=2014-11-26|accessdate=2016-01-04|website=nbcnews.com|archive-date=2021-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224090516/https://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/video-shows-cleveland-cop-shoot-12-year-old-tamir-rice-n256656|dead-url=no}}</ref>。根据事件报告的描述，在下午3时30分左右派遣警员之前，911接线员曾两次询问莱斯是[[白人|白人]]还是[[黑人|黑人]]<ref name="Cleveland police officer shot Tamir Rice immediately after leaving moving patrol car"></ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/cleveland-police-shooting-boy-with-fake-gun-dies-after-being-shot-by-ohio-officer-9878700.html|title=12-year-old boy playing with fake gun dies after being shot by Ohio police|website=independent.co.uk|first=Lizzie|last=Dearden|date=2014-11-24|accessdate=2016-01-04|archive-date=2020-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200611102826/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/cleveland-police-shooting-boy-with-fake-gun-dies-after-being-shot-by-ohio-officer-9878700.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。真实的电话录音则显示：911接线员曾三次询问持枪者是黑人或者白人。但是，报警人当时只描述了莱斯衣服的[[颜色|颜色]]<ref name="youtube.com">{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HDaOG90Dahg|title=911 caller: 12-year-old boy shot by US police probably had a 'fake' gun|website=YouTube|date=2014-11-24|author=The Telegraph|accessdate=2016-01-04|archive-date=2021-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210520104905/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HDaOG90Dahg|dead-url=no}}</ref>。报警人随后离开了露台，而莱斯不久后便进入露台并坐在其中<ref name="Video Shows Cleveland Cop Shoot 12-Year-Old Tamir Rice Within Seconds"></ref>。

根据事发当天克里夫兰巡逻警察协会主席杰弗里·福尔莫（{{lang|en|Jeffrey Follmer}}）接受媒体采访时所说：“（鲁曼和贾姆柏克）将车停在了停车场并且看见一些人坐在公园隔壁的露台里。（鲁曼）看到桌上有一把黑色的手枪，并且看到莱斯将枪从桌子上拿起来插在了腰间。”<ref name="cleveland.com">{{cite web|url=http://www.cleveland.com/metro/index.ssf/2014/11/cleveland_police_officer_shoot_6.html|title=Cleveland police officer shoots 12-year-old boy carrying BB gun|first=Cory|last=Shaffer|date=2014-11-22|accessdate=2016-01-04|website=cleveland.com|archive-date=2019-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190114085244/https://www.cleveland.com/metro/index.ssf/2014/11/cleveland_police_officer_shoot_6.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>  在同一天，克里夫兰副总警监汤姆巴（{{lang|en|Tomba}}）表示：“当时警察走出车外并且让莱斯举起双手。莱斯将手伸向腰间、拔出手枪。（鲁曼）向莱斯射击两次。”根据副总警监汤姆巴的描述：“莱斯没有口头或者身体上威胁两名警察。”<ref name="Fitzsimmons"></ref><ref name="BBC24"></ref><ref name="cleveland.com"></ref> 11月26日，也就是监控录像被公开的当天，副总警监汤姆巴表示：“当莱斯向警车走来时，鲁曼在车中向其喊话三次，要求他的双手处于可见状态。”<ref name="Washington Post"></ref>  整个事件的发生过程不超过2秒<ref name="Tamir Rice shooting video shows cop shot him within 2 seconds">{{cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2014/11/27/us/video-shows-cleveland-officer-shot-tamir-rice-2-seconds-after-pulling-up-next-to-him.html|title=Video Shows Cleveland Officer Shot Boy in 2 Seconds|date=2014-11-27|accessdate=2016-01-04|first=Emma|last=Fitzsimmons|website=New York Times|archive-date=2021-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127070849/https://www.nytimes.com/2014/11/27/us/video-shows-cleveland-officer-shot-tamir-rice-2-seconds-after-pulling-up-next-to-him.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。两名警察随后发现莱斯的手枪为[[软气枪|仿真枪]]，是真枪的仿制品，用于射击非致命性的[[BB彈|BB弹]]。但是枪口上的橙色标记已被移除。莱斯于事发后第二天在城市健康医疗中心（{{lang|en|MetroHealth Medical Center}}）去世。院方表示：莱斯的死因是由于子弹击中躯干，造成主要的血管、肠道和骨盆破裂<ref name="MacDonald"></ref>。凯霍加郡（{{lang|en|Cuyahoga County}}）医学鉴定官员的[[尸检|尸检]]报告显示：莱斯身高5英尺7英寸（170厘米），体重195磅（88千克）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wkyc.com/story/news/local/cleveland/2014/12/12/tamir-rice-autopsy-report-released/20300691/|title=Tamir Rice autopsy report released|author=WKYC Staff, WKYC|date=2014-12-20|publisher=WKYC|accessdate=2016-01-04|website=WKYC}}</ref>。

在公众和莱斯家庭的压力下，警方在2014年11月26日公布了一份没有声音的[[闭路电视|监控视频]]<ref name="Protests break out in Cleveland over Tamir Rice shooting, Ferguson grand jury decision"></ref>。视频显示：莱斯在公园中走动，偶尔将持有被认为是玩具枪的右手和手臂前伸，与其他人用手机通话和曾坐在露台中烧烤桌的旁边。视频中还显示：一辆巡逻[[警车|警车]]高速从公园的草坪驶来，突然停在露台边。鲁曼跳出警车并立刻从距离莱斯10英尺（3米）远处向莱斯开枪<ref name="Cleveland police officer shot Tamir Rice immediately after leaving moving patrol car"></ref><ref name="Video Shows Cleveland Cop Shoot 12-Year-Old Tamir Rice Within Seconds"></ref><ref name="Video: Cop shot boy seconds after encountering him">{{cite web|url=https://news.yahoo.com/cleveland-release-video-boy-shot-officer-110012912.html|title=Video: Cop shot boy seconds after encountering him|first=Mark|last=Gillispie|website=Yahoo|date=2014-11-26|accessdate=2016-01-04|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151231100424/http://news.yahoo.com/cleveland-release-video-boy-shot-officer-110012912.html|archivedate=2015-12-31}}</ref>。[[法官|法官]]罗纳德·阿德林（{{lang|en|Ronald B. Adrine}}）的[[判决书|判决书]]中显示：“本[[法庭|法庭]]仍然对于这个事件在如此短的时间内变成致命事件而感到震惊...视频中，鲁曼警官和贾姆柏克警官居然在车还没停稳的情况下就开始向莱斯开枪。”<ref name="scribd.com"></ref>

两名警官均没有在射击后对莱斯进行抢救<ref>{{cite news| url=http://nymag.com/daily/intelligencer/2014/11/cops-who-shot-tamir-rice-didnt-give-first-aid.html| author=Caroline Bankoff| title=Cops Who Shot Tamir Rice Didn't Bother to Give Him First Aid| work=New York| date=2014-11-29| accessdate=2016-01-04| archive-date=2018-07-10| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180710225201/http://nymag.com/daily/intelligencer/2014/11/cops-who-shot-tamir-rice-didnt-give-first-aid.html| dead-url=no}}</ref>。大约4分钟后，一名警探和一名在附近调查[[银行|银行]]抢劫案的[[联邦调查局|联邦调查局]]探员赶到了现场并对莱斯进行了抢救。又过了3分钟，医务人员赶到了现场，并将莱斯送往城市健康医疗中心（{{lang|en|MetroHealth Medical Center}}）<ref name="Police Who Shot 12-Year-Old Tamir Rice Did Not Give Him First Aid">{{cite web|url=http://talkingpointsmemo.com/livewire/police-tamir-rice-no-first-aid|title=Police Who Shot 12-Year-Old Tamir Rice Did Not Give Him First Aid|first=Brendan|last=James|date=2014-11-28|accessdate=2016-01-04|website=Talking Points Memo|archive-date=2021-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211225225409/https://talkingpointsmemo.com/livewire/police-tamir-rice-no-first-aid|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="12-Year-Old Boy's Fatal Shooting By Cops Could Have Been Avoided: Family">{{cite web|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/11/27/12-year-old-boys-fatal-shooting_n_6231666.html?ir=Crime|title=12-Year-Old Boy's Fatal Shooting By Cops Could Have Been Avoided: Family|date=2014-11-27|accessdate=2016-01-04|first=Mark|last=Gillispie|website=Huffington Post|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924211302/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/11/27/12-year-old-boys-fatal-shooting_n_6231666.html?ir=Crime|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Video shows Cleveland officer shooting 12-year-old Tamir Rice within seconds">{{cite web|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/news/post-nation/wp/2014/11/26/officials-release-video-names-in-fatal-police-shooting-of-12-year-old-cleveland-boy/|title=Video shows Cleveland officer shooting 12-year-old Tamir Rice within seconds|date=2014-11-26|accessdate=2016-01-04|website=Washington Post|first1=Elahe|last1=Izadi|first2=Peter|last2=Holley|archive-date=2021-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227170312/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/post-nation/wp/2014/11/26/officials-release-video-names-in-fatal-police-shooting-of-12-year-old-cleveland-boy/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

莱斯的母亲称那把玩具枪是在警察到达之前的几分钟前一位朋友送给莱斯的。[[枪杀|枪杀]]事件发生后，警察当时将她按在地上并且给她14岁的女儿带上了手铐。警察还威胁莱斯的母亲如果她不冷静下来就要将她[[逮捕|逮捕]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2014/12/09/us/family-of-boy-killed-by-cleveland-officer-to-pursue-criminal-case.html|title=Family of Boy Killed by Cleveland Officer to Pursue Criminal Case|website=New York Times|date=2014-12-09|accessdate=2016-01-04|first=Richard|last=Oppel Jr|archive-date=2021-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210210084612/https://www.nytimes.com/2014/12/09/us/family-of-boy-killed-by-cleveland-officer-to-pursue-criminal-case.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

另一份由东北[[俄亥俄|俄亥俄]]传媒集团（{{lang|en|Northeast Ohio Media Group}}）获取并在2015年1月7日发布的视频显示：枪击发生两分钟之后，在尝试跑向弟弟的途中，莱斯14岁的姐姐被带着手铐强行按在地上，随后被关进了警车。视频还显示，枪击过后4分钟，警方才对莱斯进行抢救。<ref name=HuffPo.newVideo>{{cite web|last1=McCormack|first1=Simon|title=New Video Of Tamir Rice Shooting Shows Police Arresting Sister, Delaying First Aid|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2015/01/08/new-video-tamir-rice_n_6436040.html|work=The Huffington Post|date=2015-01-08|accessdate=2016-01-04|archive-date=2017-03-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170313151956/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2015/01/08/new-video-tamir-rice_n_6436040.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

