枪击事件后，媒体公布了两名警员的背景资料。两人均被给予行政休假的处分。<ref name="Fox8">{{cite web|url=http://fox8.com/2015/06/05/officers-involved-in-tamir-rice-shooting-remain-on-the-job-away-from-public/|title=Officers involved in Tamir Rice shooting remain on the job, away from public|website=Fox8|date=2015-06-05|accessdate=2016-01-04|author=Fox8webcentral|archive-date=2020-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200109031904/https://fox8.com/2015/06/05/officers-involved-in-tamir-rice-shooting-remain-on-the-job-away-from-public/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2015年12月28日，陪审团裁定两名警员无罪。<ref name="Family of Tamir Rice, 12-year-old Cleveland boy fatally shot by police, question cops' training, call death avoidable">{{cite web|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/news/national/tamir-rice-family-question-cops-training-shooting-article-1.2025828|title=Family of Tamir Rice, 12-year-old Cleveland boy fatally shot by police, question cops' training, call death avoidable|first=Meg|last=Wagner|website=New York Daily News|date=2014-11-27|accessdate=2016-01-04|archive-date=2016-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160205003550/http://www.nydailynews.com/news/national/tamir-rice-family-question-cops-training-shooting-article-1.2025828|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 蒂莫西·鲁曼（{{lang|en|Timothy Loehmann}}） ===
开枪射杀莱斯的警员鲁曼与2014年3月开始任职克里夫兰警局。2012年，他曾在位于克里夫兰以南13迈（21公里）的{{link-en|独立市 (俄亥俄州)|Independence, Ohio|独立市}}警察局工作过5个月，包括在警察学校学习的4个月。

事件发生后，在一份被公开的独立市[[人力资源|人力资源]]主管的备忘录中，独立市副总警监吉姆·波拉克（{{lang|en|Jim Polak}}）写道：考虑到自己情绪容易波动，不适合担任警察的工作，为了避免被警局辞退，鲁曼选择了主动辞职。波拉克提到鲁曼难以遵守“基本的工作要求”。他特意引用了在一次射击训练中发生的“情绪爆发的危险行为”。在那次训练中，鲁曼的训练成绩很不理想。并且，很明显地，由于情感问题的影响，他表现的“心不在焉且十分伤感”。那份备忘录的结论部分写道：“如果单独拿出来看，这些事件都不是十分严重。但是，当它们被联系起来看时，这些事件说明他不够成熟、行为轻率且不能遵守指令。我不认为时间或者训练能够改善或者矫正这些问题。”随后，又有报道指出，在雇佣鲁曼之前，克里夫兰警察部门从来没有复核过其在独立市的个人档案<ref name="LATimes.unfit"></ref>。

=== 弗兰克·贾姆柏克（{{lang|en|Frank Garmback}}） ===
贾姆柏克是当时警车的驾驶员。他自2008年起就在克里夫兰警局工作。2014年，克里夫兰市向一名当地妇女支付了10万美元用以和解一项针对贾姆柏克过分使用武力的指控。在那名妇女的指控中，贾姆柏克“冲向她并且从背后掐住她的[[脖子|脖子]]、将她放倒在地、扭住她的[[手腕|手腕]]并殴打她”，“这些轻率的、荒唐的且蓄意的过分使用武力造成了她[[身体|身体]]受伤”。当时，这名妇女由于一辆车挡住了她家的车道而报警求助<ref name="Cleveland.com.paid">{{cite web|url=http://www.cleveland.com/court-justice/index.ssf/2014/12/cleveland_paid_out_100000_to_w.html#incart_river|title=Cleveland paid out $100,000 to woman involving excessive force lawsuit against officer in Tamir Rice shooting|first=John|last=Caniglia|date=2014-12-04|accessdate=2016-01-04|website=cleveland.com|archive-date=2019-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190216163653/https://www.cleveland.com/court-justice/index.ssf/2014/12/cleveland_paid_out_100000_to_w.html#incart_river|dead-url=no}}</ref>。这个和解案件并没有出现在贾姆柏克警局档案中<ref name="Cleveland.com.scathing">{{cite web|url=http://www.cleveland.com/top-5/2014/12/justice_departments_scathing_r.html|title=Justice Department's scathing review; another excessive force lawsuit|first=Ray|last=Jablonski|date=2014-12-04|accessdate=2016-01-04|website=cleveland.com|archive-date=2021-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210502075717/https://www.cleveland.com/top-5/2014/12/justice_departments_scathing_r.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 事后发展 ==

=== 调查 ===
鲁曼和贾姆柏克均向[[克里夫兰警察局|克里夫兰警察局]]提交了事件的报告。报告中，两人声称他们正在寻找更多的事件目击者，包括事件发生以前公园中和莱斯走在一起的一位男性。

2015年1月1日，[[美联社|美联社]]报道称：[[克里夫兰警局|克里夫兰警局]]正在寻求第三方来调查事件的经过和应对今后有可能发生的所有类似事件。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2015/01/01/tamir-rice-death-probe_n_6404396.html|title=Cleveland Seeks Outside Probe In Tamir Rice Shooting|website=Huffington Post|date=2015-01-01|accessdate=2016-01-04|author=Associate Press|archive-date=2016-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160210051813/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2015/01/01/tamir-rice-death-probe_n_6404396.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2015年5月15日，《琼斯母亲》杂志称：在莱斯死后6个月，尽管警方宣布他们基本上对于事件的经过有了结论，两名涉事的警官却从没有接受过来自凯霍加郡警长办公室调查员的问询。该报道还称当时驾驶警车的贾姆柏克并没有接受刑事[[犯罪|犯罪]]的调查。<ref name=MoJo>{{cite web|last1=Lee|first1=Jaeah|title=It’s Been 6 Months Since Tamir Rice Died, and the Cop Who Killed Him Still Hasn't Been Questioned|url=http://www.motherjones.com/politics/2015/05/tamir-rice-investigation-cleveland-police|website=Mother Jones|publisher=Mother Jones and the Foundation for National Progres|accessdate=2015-05-18|date=2015-05-15|archive-date=2021-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210210084613/https://www.motherjones.com/politics/2015/05/tamir-rice-investigation-cleveland-police/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2015年6月3日，凯霍加郡警长办公室发表了一份声明。声明称：针对警察射杀莱斯事件的调查已经完成，他们已经将调查结果转交给了公诉人蒂姆·麦克金蒂（{{lang|en|Tim McGinty}}）。麦克金蒂将会审阅这些报告并且决定是否将这些报告呈现给陪审团<ref name="auto"></ref>。作为对于市民情愿的回应，2015年6月11日，市法院[[法官|法官]]罗纳德·阿德林（{{lang|en|Ronald B. Adrine}}）同意“鲁曼应该受到多项罪名的指控，其中最严重的一项是[[谋杀|谋杀]]，其他还包括[[误杀|误杀]]、怂恿杀人、[[过失杀人|过失杀人]]和[[渎职|渎职]]”。阿德林法官还发现一些以“过失杀人和渎职”起诉贾姆柏克的合理可能性（{{lang|en|probable cause}}）。他的观点被转达至市和凯霍加郡公诉人麦克金蒂那里。当时，麦克金蒂并没有决定是否将证据呈现给陪审团<ref name="The Atlantic">{{cite web | url=http://www.theatlantic.com/politics/archive/2015/06/tamir-rice-case-cleveland/395420/ | title='Probable Cause' in the Killing of Tamir Rice | work=The Atlantic | date=2015-06-11 | accessdate=2015-06-12 | last=Graham | first=David | archive-date=2021-02-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210210084527/https://www.theatlantic.com/politics/archive/2015/06/tamir-rice-case-cleveland/395420/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==== 报告 ====
2015年6月13日，凯霍加郡公诉人麦克金蒂公开了一份节选后224页的调查报告<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.latimes.com/nation/nationnow/la-na-nn-tamir-rice-investigation-documents-20150613-story.html|title=Tamir Rice investigation released by Cleveland prosecutors|website=Los Angeles Times|date=2015-06-13|accessdate=2015-10-04|first=Jaeah|last=Lee|archive-date=2021-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210613085218/https://www.latimes.com/nation/nationnow/la-na-nn-tamir-rice-investigation-documents-20150613-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。这份报告包括了27人的证词，其中包括莱斯的老师、朋友和报警人。鲁曼和贾姆柏克拒绝接受讯问<ref name="Cleveland.com.witness">{{cite web|url=http://www.cleveland.com/metro/index.ssf/2015/06/witness_accounts_in_tamir_rice.html|title=Witness accounts in Tamir Rice investigation paint vivid picture of events|first=Rich|last=Exner|date=2015-06-13|accessdate=2015-10-04|website=cleveland.com|archive-date=2019-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190301053819/https://www.cleveland.com/metro/index.ssf/2015/06/witness_accounts_in_tamir_rice.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

报告中，多名证人证实在警察开枪之前没有听到任何警告。这与警局的申明中所述鲁曼曾三次警告莱斯“举起双手”相违背<ref name="Cleveland.com.bigstory">{{cite web|url=http://www.cleveland.com/metro/index.ssf/2015/06/tamir_rice_investigation_relea.html|title=Tamir Rice investigation released: The Big Story|date=2015-06-13|accessdate=2016-01-04|website=cleveland.com|first=Ida|last=Lieszkovszky|archive-date=2015-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150614031553/http://www.cleveland.com/metro/index.ssf/2015/06/tamir_rice_investigation_relea.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

凯霍加郡公诉人办公室收到了两份第三方专家的调查报告。一份来自前[[联邦调查局|联邦调查局]]探员金伯利·克劳福德（{{lang|en|Kimberly Crawford}}），另一份来自[[科羅拉多州|科罗拉多]]公诉人S·拉玛尔·西姆斯（{{lang|en|S. Lamar Sims}}）。两份报告均认为在事件发生时，射杀莱斯的选择是合理的。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/10/11/us-usa-police-ohio-idUSKCN0S502O20151011|title=Reports find shooting of Tamir Rice reasonable|date=2015-10-11|accessdate=2016-01-04|first=Kim|last=Palmer|website=Reuters|archive-date=2015-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151018224325/http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/10/11/us-usa-police-ohio-iduskcn0s502o20151011|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

=== 警方的矛盾解释 ===
下面4处解释的警方部分均来自副总警监艾德·汤姆巴（{{lang|en|Ed Tomba}}）在监控视频被公布之前的表述：<ref name="cleveland.com"></ref>
# 警方称莱斯当时与其他人一起坐在桌边。视频显示莱斯是独自一人。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailykos.com/story/2015/01/08/1356312/-I-hereby-charge-Timothy-Loehmann-the-Cleveland-PD-with-the-murder-of-12-year-old-Tamir-Rice|title=I hereby charge Timothy Loehmann and the Cleveland PD with the murder of 12-year-old Tamir Rice|website=Daily Kos|date=2015-01-08|first=Shaun|last=King|accessdate=2016-01-04|archive-date=2016-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161222224052/http://www.dailykos.com/story/2015/01/08/1356312/-I-hereby-charge-Timothy-Loehmann-the-Cleveland-PD-with-the-murder-of-12-year-old-Tamir-Rice|dead-url=no}}</ref>
# 警方称在警车驶近的过程中，他们看到莱斯拿起枪并插在了[[腰带|腰带]]上。视频并不能证实这一点<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/video-shows-cleveland-cop-shoot-12-year-old-tamir-rice-n256656|title=Video Shows Cleveland Cop Shoot 12-Year-Old Tamir Rice Within Seconds|first=Tracy|last=Connor|date=2014-11-26|accessdate=2016-01-04|website=NBC News|archive-date=2021-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224090516/https://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/video-shows-cleveland-cop-shoot-12-year-old-tamir-rice-n256656|dead-url=no}}</ref>。阿德林法官称：视频并没有显示在警车靠近时莱斯将枪拿在手里<ref name="scribd.com"></ref>。
# 警方称莱斯将手伸向腰间并取出枪，随后被鲁曼射杀。视频显示，莱斯并没有去拔枪<ref name="msnbc.com">{{cite web|url=http://www.msnbc.com/all-in/watch/how-reliable-is-police-testimony--365827139616|title=How reliable is police testimony?|website=MSNBC|date=2014-12-01|accessdate=2016-01-04|archive-date=2021-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210213055428/https://www.msnbc.com/all-in/watch/how-reliable-is-police-testimony--365827139616|dead-url=no}}</ref>。视频中，倒地之前，莱斯双手提住上衣并且露出了仿真枪。
# 警方形容仿真枪看起来很逼真，后来解释为由于仿真枪上的醒目标识缺失而造成了误会<ref name="dailykos.com"></ref>。但是，警员并没有看到莱斯向他们挥舞手枪或者将枪口指向他们，从而也就不可能看到枪头是否有仿真枪的标识<ref name="dailykos.com"></ref>。

=== 非正常死亡诉讼 ===
2014年12月5日，莱斯的亲人以“非正常死亡”在[[美国俄亥俄北区联邦地区法院|美国俄亥俄北区联邦地区法院]]对鲁曼、贾姆柏克和克里夫兰市提起[[诉讼|诉讼]]。在长达8页的起诉书中，鲁曼和贾姆柏克被指控行为“不理智、不负责且鲁莽”，如果两位[[被告|被告]]“当时合理的接近莱斯、调查莱斯手中的枪，他们就毫无疑问的能够发现...那把枪其实是仿真枪，而且莱斯其实并未成年。”起诉中还包括了针对克里夫兰市没能适当地训练两名警官、疏于核查独立市针对鲁曼的备忘录的指控<ref name="Family of Tamir Rice, 12-Year-Old Shot By Cop, Files Wrongful Death Suit">{{cite web|url=http://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/family-tamir-rice-12-year-old-shot-cop-files-wrongful-n262661|title=Family of Tamir Rice, 12-Year-Old Shot By Cop, Files Wrongful Death Suit|website=NBC News|date=2014-12-05|accessdate=2016-01-04|archive-date=2021-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210210084519/https://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/family-tamir-rice-12-year-old-shot-cop-files-wrongful-n262661|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Tamir Rice's family files wrongful death suit against Cleveland police officers">{{cite web|url=http://fox8.com/2014/12/05/tamir-rices-family-files-wrongful-death-suit-against-cleveland-police/|title=Tamir Rice’s family files wrongful death suit against Cleveland police officers|website=Fox8|first1=Jen|last1=Steer|first2=Peggy|last2=Gallek|date=2014-12-05|accessdate=2016-01-04|archive-date=2020-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200110201621/https://fox8.com/2014/12/05/tamir-rices-family-files-wrongful-death-suit-against-cleveland-police/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Tamir Rice's family files wrongful death lawsuit after fatal shooting of 12-year-old in Cleveland">{{cite web|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/news/post-nation/wp/2014/12/05/tamir-rices-family-files-wrongful-death-lawsuit-after-fatal-shooting-of-12-year-old-in-cleveland/|title=Tamir Rice’s family files wrongful death lawsuit after fatal shooting of 12-year-old in Cleveland|date=2014-12-05|first=Sarah|last=Larimer|website=W ashington Post|access-date=2016-01-04|archive-date=2021-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210210084712/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/post-nation/wp/2014/12/05/tamir-rices-family-files-wrongful-death-lawsuit-after-fatal-shooting-of-12-year-old-in-cleveland/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
一个[[美国联邦地区法院|联邦地区法院]]将会与2015年6月召开听证会来决定是否由于刑事调查尚未结束来延迟莱斯亲人的诉讼<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wkyc.com/story/news/local/cleveland/2015/05/19/judge-to-consider-delaying-lawsuit-against-cops-who-shot-tamir-rice/27575999/|title=Judge to consider delaying lawsuit against cops who shot Tamir Rice|date=2015-05-19|accessdate=2016-01-04|website=WKYC|author=AP/WKYC Staff}}{{dead link|date=2018年5月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。

=== 游行示威 ===
事件发生后不久，克里夫兰就爆发了规模有限的[[游行|游行]]示威和公众抗议行为。但是2014年11月25日，在大[[陪审团|陪审团]]裁定不起诉[[邁克爾·布朗命案|枪杀麦克·布朗]]（{{lang|en|Michael Brown}}）的警察之后的第二天，克里夫兰抗议游行活动的规模开始变大。当天大约有200名抗议者从公共广场（{{lang|en|Public Square}}）行进至克里夫兰纪念岸边道（{{lang|en|Cleveland Memorial Shoreway}}），造成了后者被临时关闭<ref name="Protests break out in Cleveland over Tamir Rice shooting, Ferguson grand jury decision"></ref><ref name="Video shows Cleveland officer shooting 12-year-old Tamir Rice within seconds"></ref>。莱斯的亲人呼吁抗议者保持冷静：“再一次地，我们希望大家保持冷静。请和平地、负责任的进行游行示威。”<ref name="Family of 12-year-old black boy shot and killed by white police officer for holding a toy gun plead with supporters to stay peaceful amid fears of more violent protests">{{cite web|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2852119/Family-12-year-old-black-boy-shot-killed-white-police-officer-holding-toy-gun-plead-supporters-stay-peaceful-amid-fears-violent-protests.html|title=Tamir Rice's family plead with supporters to stay peaceful amid fears of more violent protests - Daily Mail Online|website=Daily Mail|date=2014-11-27|accessdate=2015-10-04|first1=Nick|last1=Fagge|first2=Lydia|last2=Warren|archive-date=2021-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210228103318/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2852119/Family-12-year-old-black-boy-shot-killed-white-police-officer-holding-toy-gun-plead-supporters-stay-peaceful-amid-fears-violent-protests.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2015年12月5日，[[俄亥俄州|俄亥俄州]]州长[[約翰·卡西奇|约翰·卡西奇]]组建了一支队伍专门应对类似于莱斯事件之后的这种警民关系。<ref name="Kasich forms task force to improve police-community relations">{{cite web|url=http://www.daytondailynews.com/news/news/local/kasich-forms-task-force-to-improve-police-communit/njMSk/|title=Kasich police commission Ferguson Beavercreek|website=Dayton Daily News|date=201-12-05|first=Chris|last=Stewart|accessdate=2016-01-04|archive-date=2016-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160825012719/http://www.daytondailynews.com/news/news/local/kasich-forms-task-force-to-improve-police-communit/njMSk/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

莱斯的死亡被认为是一系列警察杀人案件中的一起。这些案件“激发”了全国范围内“[[黑人的命也是命|黑人的命也是命]]”运动。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Williams|first1=Yohuru|title=You're Nobody 'Till Somebody Kills You: Baltimore, Freddie Gray and the Problem of History|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/yohuru-williams/youre-nobody-till-somebod_b_7167028.html|work=[[The_Huffington_Post|The Huffington Post]]|accessdate=2015-05-29|date=2015-04-29|archive-date=2015-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150529012247/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/yohuru-williams/youre-nobody-till-somebod_b_7167028.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Fields|first1=Liz|title=After Walter Scott Killing, Black Lives Matter Movement Calls For Citizen Oversight of Police|url=https://news.vice.com/article/after-walter-scott-killing-black-lives-matter-movement-calls-for-citizen-oversight-of-police|work=Vice (magazine)|accessdate=2015-05-26|date=2015-04-10|archive-date=2015-05-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150526112703/https://news.vice.com/article/after-walter-scott-killing-black-lives-matter-movement-calls-for-citizen-oversight-of-police|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://colorofchange.org/press/releases/2014/12/22/activists-blast-nypd-attempts-silence-movement-cha/|title=Activists Blast NYPD Attempts to Silence Movement for Change|date=2014-12-22|accessdate=2016-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305211244/http://colorofchange.org/press/releases/2014/12/22/activists-blast-nypd-attempts-silence-movement-cha/|archive-date=2016-03-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

=== 媒体报道 ===
这个事件得到了美国全国乃至全世界媒体的关注。其中部分的原因是其发生时间距离发生在[[密苏里州|密苏里州]][[弗格森_(密蘇里州)|弗格森市]]的[[邁克爾·布朗命案|麦克·布朗命案]]、发生在[[史泰登岛|纽约市史泰登岛]]的[[埃里克·加纳死亡案|埃里克·加纳死亡案]]、发生在[[布鲁克林区|纽约市布鲁克林]]的阿凯·格利死亡案和发生在[[俄亥俄州|俄亥俄州]][[代顿_(俄亥俄州)|代顿市]]的约翰·克劳福德三世死亡案以及由这些事件引发的骚乱事件很接近。

东北俄亥俄传媒集团由于公布了莱斯父母的犯罪记录而受到了指责。<ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.slate.com/blogs/the_slatest/2014/11/28/cleveland_paper_defends_publishing_details_about_tamir_rice_s_criminal_background.html| first=Daniel| last=Politi| title=Cleveland Paper Thinks You Should Know Tamir Rice’s Father Has Abused Women| work=Slate| date=2014-11-28| accessdate=2016-01-04| archive-date=2018-10-07| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181007114522/http://www.slate.com/blogs/the_slatest/2014/11/28/cleveland_paper_defends_publishing_details_about_tamir_rice_s_criminal_background.html| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/11/26/tamir-rice-father_n_6227312.html| first=Nick| last=Wing| title=Police Gunned Down A 12-Year-Old And Somehow Local News Decided To Run This Story| work=The Huffington Post| date=2014-11-26| accessdate=2016-01-04| archive-date=2019-03-14| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190314142858/https://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/11/26/tamir-rice-father_n_6227312.html| dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 葬礼 ===
莱斯的[[葬礼|葬礼]]于2014年12月3日在[[西乃山|西乃山]][[浸信会|浸信会]][[教堂|教堂]]（{{lang|en|Mount Sinai Baptist Church}}）举行。大约250人参加了他的葬礼。葬礼上，莱斯被描述为“一个有做[[布丁|布丁]]天分的人和一个喜爱[[画画|画画]]、热爱[[篮球|篮球]]、积极参与学校鼓队且受欢迎的孩子。”莱斯的亲人指责鲁曼在造成莱斯的死亡的事件中反应过于迅速。<ref name="Tamir Rice's family blasts police at boy’s Cleveland funeral">{{cite web|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/news/crime/tamir-rice-family-blasts-police-boy-cleveland-funeral-article-1.2032033|first=Nicole|last=Hensley|title=Tamir Rice’s family blasts police at boy’s Cleveland funeral|website=Daily News|date=2015-12-03|accessdate=2016-01-04|archive-date=2021-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210502040819/https://www.nydailynews.com/news/crime/tamir-rice-family-blasts-police-boy-cleveland-funeral-article-1.2032033|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="NBC News">{{cite web|url=http://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/tears-funeral-cleveland-boy-tamir-rice-shot-cop-n260741|title=Tears at Funeral for Cleveland Boy Tamir Rice Shot by Cop|website=NBC News|date=2014-12-03|accessdate=2016-01-04|archive-date=2021-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210210084616/https://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/tears-funeral-cleveland-boy-tamir-rice-shot-cop-n260741|dead-url=no}}</ref>

